Name: Deep Voyage
About the game: Beautiful mermaid sets off for her voyage in the depths of sea. Help her to win a royal garden design competition in an Underwater Kingdom. Her rivals in the contest are strong and it will be difficult to excel them. Complete exciting levels, solve puzzles, help mermaid to find all she needs to make your sea-garden perfect. Deep Voyage is a new truly marvelous collapse game which will lead you through more than 200 levels of fun.
